The curated content in this directory — biosensor designs (`data/biosensors/`),
the safe-chassis catalog (`data/chassis/`), the genetic-parts registry
(`data/parts/`), and the legacy in-vitro assay set (`data/legacy-assays/`) — is
licensed under CC BY 4.0: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

You are free to share and adapt this data for any purpose, provided you give
appropriate credit.

Note: the underlying biological sequences, genetic parts, and sensing modules
referenced here originate from the primary scientific literature and registries
cited in each record's `provenance` field, and remain subject to their original
sources and terms. Designs marked `status: "template"` combine individually
published parts into a circuit pattern and are not validated devices.

(The application source code in this repository is licensed under the MIT
License — see the top-level `LICENSE`.)
